1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:04,200
And now, for our final event of the day.

2
00:00:04,200 --> 00:00:06,160
The class relay race.

3
00:00:06,920 --> 00:00:09,200
Go get 'em!

4
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:10,800
Good luck, guys!

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:13,800
Just don't get hurt.

6
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:17,520
Oh, man.

7
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:19,240
No time for a proper warm-up.

8
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:21,680
Can't help it. Being on the sports committee is a full-time job.

9
00:00:21,680 --> 00:00:23,920
Warming up is crucial, especially since...

10
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:26,680
Alright, alright! I'm in great shape.

11
00:00:26,680 --> 00:00:28,640
What if you get injured again?

12
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:30,320
Ugh, quit nagging.

13
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:33,640
Just don't hold me back.

14
00:00:35,720 --> 00:00:37,120
Right back at you.

15
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:41,400
Will the runners please take their marks?

16
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,720
On your marks.

17
00:00:46,720 --> 00:00:48,120
Get set!

18
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:52,160
I can't believe who's in the lead.

19
00:00:52,160 --> 00:00:53,320
It's the Blue Team!

20
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:56,040
Will lady luck be on our side today?

21
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:06,080
No, no, no!

22
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,640
Damn it.

23
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:10,040
What are you doing, you idiot?

24
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,760
Shake it off!

25
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:34,880
Running feels so good.

26
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,120
Iijima Hinata?

27
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:45,160
- Sorry, Kono Mizuki.
- You were right.

28
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,040
Leave it to your big brother.

29
00:02:01,700 --> 00:02:03,200
The Blue Team takes first place!

30
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:07,450
What an incredible performance!
